                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • If [ IsEmpty(Shades_via_Order_FK::Style Name) ]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Commit Records/Requests
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Halt Script

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • If [ IsEmpty(Shades_via_Order_FK::HeightToSoftCasuals) and Shades_via_Order_FK::ifPoufy = "yes" ]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Show Custom Dialog [ Title: "Message"; Message: "This is a poufy style, you must select an option from the Poufy drop down"; Default Button: “OK”, Commit: “Yes” ]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Go to Field [ Shades_via_Order_FK::HeightToSoftCasuals ] [ Select/perform ]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Halt Script
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • End If
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Freeze Window

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • Select Window [ Name: "shades" ]

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • Show Custom Dialog [ Title: "Message"; Message: "You must first view the invoice in order to proceed."; Default Button: “OK”, Commit: “Yes” ]
